    "To visually demonstrate the differences between this review and existing work, Table 7 provides a horizontal comparison across three dimensions of time span, research scope, and core contributions.",
    "Early surveys primarily focused on the application of traditional Machine Learning and Deep Learning in SE [96,138,153].",
